Robert Darène https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Dar%C3%A8ne 0 Robert Darène (10 January 1914 – 15 January 2016) was a French actor, film director and screenwriter. He appeared in twelve films between 1934 and 1959, and directed nine films between 1951 and 1963.
